verbose_text: CX3CR1 expression levels distinguished three virus specific CD8 + Tmem subsets (CX3CR1 neg, CX3CR1 int, and CX3CR1 hi) in both conventional (M45-tetramer +) and inflating (M38-tetramer +) responses (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A-S2D; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), while uninfected C57BL/6 mice were devoid of CD8 + T cells expressing CX3CR1 (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A).
